01:13:43.679 --> 01:13:48.390
person in their hearing tonight

01:13:48.400 --> 01:13:51.189
that they would experience you at a new

01:13:51.199 --> 01:13:52.870
level.

01:13:52.880 --> 01:13:55.590
That they would experience the presence

01:13:55.600 --> 01:13:59.189
of the Lord at a new level,

01:13:59.199 --> 01:14:03.030
that from this day forward they'll never

01:14:03.040 --> 01:14:05.590
be the same again.

01:14:05.600 --> 01:14:08.310
That, Father, they'll tap into that

01:14:08.320 --> 01:14:10.709
river

01:14:10.719 --> 01:14:14.310
that never will run dry.

01:14:14.320 --> 01:14:17.510
Father, I thank you, Lord, that your hand

01:14:17.520 --> 01:14:20.709
of provision, your hand of comfort is

01:14:20.719 --> 01:14:23.270
over them as they've lost loved ones.

01:14:23.280 --> 01:14:25.669
They're going through the trials

01:14:25.679 --> 01:14:28.470
of life. I thank you, Father, that

01:14:28.480 --> 01:14:31.110
you give them wind in their

01:14:31.110 --> 01:14:31.120
sails

01:14:31.120 --> 01:14:32.790
and they don't get weary

01:14:32.790 --> 01:14:32.800
in

01:14:32.800 --> 01:14:35.910
well-doing.

01:14:35.920 --> 01:14:37.510
I thank you, Father, that they will

01:14:37.520 --> 01:14:39.910
finish strong.

01:14:39.920 --> 01:14:41.830
But, Father, I thank you, Lord, that

01:14:41.840 --> 01:14:44.709
those that are saying, 'I'm just not

01:14:44.719 --> 01:14:48.149
able to hear him, Brandon.

01:14:48.159 --> 01:14:52.790
I just don't know if that's

01:14:52.790 --> 01:14:52.800
him.'Father,

01:14:52.800 --> 01:14:55.189
I thank you, Lord, that you

01:14:55.199 --> 01:14:59.430
become so real to them.

01:14:59.440 --> 01:15:02.070
They'll know it just by even

01:15:02.080 --> 01:15:04.870
smelling your breath, Lord.

01:15:04.880 --> 01:15:06.950
That they would know that fragrance.

01:15:06.960 --> 01:15:12.310
They would know what you smell like,

01:15:12.320 --> 01:15:18.709
that heavenly smell.

01:15:18.719 --> 01:15:21.430
They would draw close to the Father.

01:15:21.440 --> 01:15:25.270
They would draw close to you

01:15:25.280 --> 01:15:27.350
and they would be intimate with you,

01:15:27.360 --> 01:15:31.189
Lord, knowing you

01:15:31.199 --> 01:15:33.189
are closer than a brother, that you're a

01:15:33.199 --> 01:15:35.430
friend, closer than... you're

01:15:35.440 --> 01:15:38.870
our ever-present help in a time of

01:15:38.880 --> 01:15:41.910
need.

01:15:41.920 --> 01:15:44.310
Lord, we're so grateful for every one of

01:15:44.320 --> 01:15:46.310
these people here, but God, their

01:15:46.320 --> 01:15:55.910
heart's desire is to know you more. Our

01:15:55.920 --> 01:16:01.030
heart's desire is to know you more,

01:16:01.040 --> 01:16:04.149
to seek you and to find you, to knock

01:16:04.159 --> 01:16:07.270
and the door will be opened. And we

01:16:07.280 --> 01:16:09.430
thank you, Father.

01:16:09.440 --> 01:16:11.110
Father, I thank you, Lord, that as they

01:16:11.120 --> 01:16:13.510
seek you, they'll find you. As they

01:16:13.520 --> 01:16:16.310
knock, the door will be opened unto

01:16:16.320 --> 01:16:23.750
them.

01:16:23.760 --> 01:16:25.350
Father, that they'll not question

01:16:25.360 --> 01:16:31.110
anymore, 'Is this you, Lord?

01:16:31.120 --> 01:16:34.470
Is this you,

01:16:34.470 --> 01:16:34.480
Lord?'But

01:16:34.480 --> 01:16:39.110
they'll say, 'I know this is him.

01:16:39.120 --> 01:16:44.470
I know this is him.

01:16:44.480 --> 01:16:48.630
I know this is

01:16:48.630 --> 01:16:48.640
him.'Speak

01:16:48.640 --> 01:16:50.790
to them in the midnight

01:16:50.800 --> 01:16:53.430
hour. Speak to them in their sleep. Speak

01:16:53.440 --> 01:16:55.590
to them in that still,

01:16:55.600 --> 01:16:57.990
small voice. And so as they

01:16:58.000 --> 01:17:00.790
quiet their thoughts,

01:17:00.800 --> 01:17:04.070
as they quiet their minds from running

01:17:04.080 --> 01:17:06.390
and being in a panic and a

01:17:06.390 --> 01:17:06.400
frantic...

01:17:06.400 --> 01:17:08.229
Shh.

01:17:08.239 --> 01:17:13.430
Peace be still.

01:17:13.440 --> 01:17:27.270
Peace be still.

01:17:27.280 --> 01:17:30.550
Father, we thank you, Lord.

01:17:30.560 --> 01:17:36.470
We glorify your name.

01:17:36.480 --> 01:17:38.709
We glorify

01:17:38.719 --> 01:17:43.590
your name.

01:17:43.600 --> 01:17:47.430
We glorify

01:17:47.440 --> 01:17:52.070
your name

01:18:31.199 --> 01:18:39.350
in all the earth.

01:18:39.360 --> 01:18:43.430
We magnify

01:18:43.440 --> 01:18:48.630
your name.

01:18:48.640 --> 01:18:52.550
We magnify

01:18:52.560 --> 01:18:57.750
your name.

01:18:57.760 --> 01:19:01.750
We magnify

01:19:01.760 --> 01:19:03.990
your name

01:19:04.000 --> 01:19:06.149
in all

01:19:06.159 --> 01:19:09.449
the earth.

01:19:14.480 --> 01:19:17.910
As we just yield to you,

01:19:17.920 --> 01:19:20.229
we glorify

01:19:20.239 --> 01:19:25.590
your name.

01:19:25.600 --> 01:19:29.350
We glorify

01:19:29.360 --> 01:19:37.030
your name.

01:19:37.040 --> 01:19:41.510
Thank you, Father.

01:19:41.520 --> 01:19:44.390
We magnify you.

01:19:44.400 --> 01:19:50.950
We glorify you,

01:19:55.679 --> 01:20:00.709
for you are good and your mercy endures

01:20:00.719 --> 01:20:03.430
forever.

01:20:03.440 --> 01:20:06.550
We magnify you, Father.

01:20:06.560 --> 01:20:10.070
We glorify you, Lord.

01:20:10.080 --> 01:20:13.030
And we thank you, Lord, as we come up

01:20:13.040 --> 01:20:15.990
higher in the fire.

01:20:16.000 --> 01:20:19.350
As we come up higher, Lord, out of being

01:20:19.360 --> 01:20:21.030
like these chickens, like I saw last

01:20:21.040 --> 01:20:24.390
night, being chickens, we soar like an

01:20:24.400 --> 01:20:27.270
eagle.

01:20:27.280 --> 01:20:31.030
We soar like an eagle and we give you

01:20:31.040 --> 01:20:45.669
praise, Father.

01:20:45.679 --> 01:20:48.149
This is interesting. When I was praying,

01:20:48.159 --> 01:20:49.910
when I was singing the song, I saw Jesus

01:20:49.920 --> 01:20:53.270
standing next to this beautiful

01:20:53.280 --> 01:20:55.189
brook. Looked like a

01:20:55.199 --> 01:20:56.950
river.

01:20:56.960 --> 01:21:02.310
But in this, he cast out a net

01:21:02.320 --> 01:21:04.630
and he was on the shoreline and I could

01:21:04.640 --> 01:21:06.630
see him. I was on this side and I was

01:21:06.640 --> 01:21:09.669
looking at him on that side, and he

01:21:09.679 --> 01:21:13.110
cast out a net into this water that

01:21:13.120 --> 01:21:16.070
looked transparent. It was

01:21:16.080 --> 01:21:19.750
just the most

01:21:19.750 --> 01:21:19.760
beautiful—the

01:21:19.760 --> 01:21:22.870
light was shining so much on it that it

01:21:22.880 --> 01:21:24.870
was like when you're out on a lake and

01:21:24.880 --> 01:21:26.870
you look at the reflection in the water.

01:21:26.880 --> 01:21:28.790
You know how the beads of light all come

01:21:28.800 --> 01:21:32.229
off the waves as the water's choppy?

01:21:32.239 --> 01:21:34.149
You can see the light shining on it, and

01:21:34.159 --> 01:21:37.750
you'll get a sunburn really bad

01:21:37.760 --> 01:21:39.270
when you look at that water and you can

01:21:39.280 --> 01:21:40.790
see the glistening of the light on the

01:21:40.800 --> 01:21:43.990
water. I could see that water, but he

01:21:44.000 --> 01:21:46.310
took his net and he threw it out on that

01:21:46.320 --> 01:21:52.550
water and he was drawing in a harvest,

01:21:52.560 --> 01:21:54.070
and I was watching him as he was

01:21:54.080 --> 01:21:57.350
fishing. It looked like he was fishing,

01:21:57.360 --> 01:22:00.550
but I know he wasn't fishing for

01:22:00.560 --> 01:22:03.669
fish. Couldn't have been.

01:22:03.679 --> 01:22:06.390
Maybe he was, but I never saw what was

01:22:06.400 --> 01:22:08.790
coming up out of that water. I just saw

01:22:08.800 --> 01:22:11.510
a net that was roped.

01:22:11.520 --> 01:22:14.310
It looked like a net that was like a

01:22:14.320 --> 01:22:16.550
fishing net that was thick, that had

01:22:16.560 --> 01:22:19.350
weights at the ends of it, that

01:22:19.360 --> 01:22:23.590
looked like a net, but

01:22:23.600 --> 01:22:26.629
it was white and it was thick.

01:22:26.639 --> 01:22:28.390
And he just took it and he threw it out

01:22:28.400 --> 01:22:30.950
on the water, and it had a string at the

01:22:30.960 --> 01:22:32.790
base of it. And he was

01:22:32.800 --> 01:22:35.777
fishing with that net.

01:22:37.120 --> 01:22:42.310
And I was sitting there just watching,

01:22:42.320 --> 01:22:49.910
not wondering what he was doing.

01:22:49.920 --> 01:22:53.350
He smiled,

01:22:53.360 --> 01:22:55.990
but he was fishing.

01:22:56.000 --> 01:23:00.470
And as I sang that verse

01:23:00.470 --> 01:23:00.480
about

01:23:00.480 --> 01:23:02.950
the woman at the well who was seeking—I was

01:23:02.960 --> 01:23:06.550
seeking for things that

01:23:06.560 --> 01:23:13.750
could not satisfy.

01:23:13.760 --> 01:23:15.990
And then

01:23:16.000 --> 01:23:21.110
I heard my Savior

01:23:21.110 --> 01:23:21.120
sing,

01:23:21.120 --> 01:23:25.557
'Draw from the

01:23:25.567 --> 01:23:28.229
well.'Is

01:23:28.239 --> 01:23:33.270
that how many are here right now, son?

01:23:33.280 --> 01:23:36.870
The well, drawing from the

01:23:36.880 --> 01:23:40.070
well, drawing from that major pool of

01:23:40.080 --> 01:23:51.590
water.

01:23:51.600 --> 01:23:53.830
He wants a refreshing for so many of

01:23:53.840 --> 01:23:56.229
you. But as I was listening, I could

01:23:56.239 --> 01:23:58.149
hear the people: 'I don't hear you. I

01:23:58.159 --> 01:23:59.910
don't hear you. I don't know what you

01:23:59.920 --> 01:24:01.110
want from my life. I don't know where

01:24:01.120 --> 01:24:03.030
you want me to go. I don't know if I'm

01:24:03.040 --> 01:24:04.790
supposed to take that job. I don't know

01:24:04.800 --> 01:24:07.270
if I'm supposed to move.

01:24:07.280 --> 01:24:12.229
Where do you want me to

01:24:12.229 --> 01:24:12.239
be?'There's

01:24:12.239 --> 01:24:18.310
so much of this torment

01:24:18.310 --> 01:24:18.320
because

01:24:18.320 --> 01:24:24.310
you want so badly not to miss it.

01:24:24.320 --> 01:24:26.310
'I don't want to miss it. I don't want to

01:24:26.320 --> 01:24:29.030
miss you. I don't want to go out and do

01:24:29.040 --> 01:24:31.430
anything ahead of you. I want to be in

01:24:31.440 --> 01:24:32.950
sync with you. I want to do what he's

01:24:32.960 --> 01:24:34.550
saying.

01:24:34.560 --> 01:24:36.310
Help me to go vertical. Help me to do

01:24:36.320 --> 01:24:38.070
these things, not to go horizontal. I

01:24:38.080 --> 01:24:39.669
want to

01:24:39.679 --> 01:24:43.270
follow you.'And so much so that it's

01:24:43.280 --> 01:24:46.149
becoming a torment.

01:24:46.159 --> 01:24:49.270
The fear of missing it.

01:24:56.639 --> 01:25:00.149
Fear has torment.

01:25:00.159 --> 01:25:02.470
The fear of missing it, fear of not

01:25:02.480 --> 01:25:06.310
walking out on the water.

01:25:06.320 --> 01:25:07.510
'What do you want me to do? What do you

01:25:07.520 --> 01:25:10.390
want me to

01:25:10.390 --> 01:25:10.400
do?'Should

01:25:10.400 --> 01:25:12.149
I take the job? Should I not?

01:25:12.159 --> 01:25:14.470
Should I go into the army?

01:25:14.480 --> 01:25:17.110
Should I go into service? Should I

01:25:17.120 --> 01:25:19.750
serve the country? Should I

01:25:19.760 --> 01:25:21.590
go to college in the

01:25:21.600 --> 01:25:28.229
fall?

01:25:28.239 --> 01:25:30.149
Should I move my family across the

01:25:30.159 --> 01:25:32.790
country?

01:25:32.800 --> 01:25:36.629
Where should I be, Lord?

01:25:36.639 --> 01:25:38.550
Should we sell our house? Should we not?

01:25:38.560 --> 01:25:40.950
Should we buy a new car? Should we not? There

01:25:40.950 --> 01:25:40.960
are

01:25:40.960 --> 01:25:42.550
so many things that are running

01:25:42.560 --> 01:25:44.950
through people's heads.

01:25:44.960 --> 01:25:48.149
Should I have that surgery? Lord,

01:25:48.159 --> 01:25:49.990
I'm believing for healing. Should I have

01:25:50.000 --> 01:25:51.510
that?

01:25:51.520 --> 01:25:54.229
Should I get a new body part, like

01:25:54.239 --> 01:25:55.669
a new knee or whatever you're believing

01:25:55.669 --> 01:25:55.679
for?

01:25:55.679 --> 01:25:58.470
You know, there are so many

01:25:58.480 --> 01:26:00.629
people that have so many different

01:26:00.639 --> 01:26:02.310
things they're asking, but you're

01:26:02.320 --> 01:26:03.830
tormented. You come up

01:26:03.840 --> 01:26:06.870
against that wall.

01:26:06.880 --> 01:26:08.629
'What if? What

01:26:08.639 --> 01:26:10.229
if?'That's

01:26:10.239 --> 01:26:13.990
what I'm hearing.

01:26:14.000 --> 01:26:19.590
But it's drawing from the well

01:26:19.600 --> 01:26:22.950
that never runs dry in that place of

01:26:22.960 --> 01:26:25.110
worship—that's

01:26:25.120 --> 01:26:28.229
where your answer

01:26:28.229 --> 01:26:28.239
is.

01:26:28.239 --> 01:26:31.030
It's not in the 'what if.'It's not in

01:26:31.040 --> 01:26:32.950
that torment.

01:26:32.960 --> 01:26:33.910
'What are we going to do? What are we

01:26:33.920 --> 01:26:34.709
going to

01:26:34.709 --> 01:26:34.719
do?'It's

01:26:34.719 --> 01:26:36.870
just always the echo inside of

01:26:36.880 --> 01:26:38.310
your head at night when you're trying to

01:26:38.320 --> 01:26:41.030
sleep, that peace

01:26:41.030 --> 01:26:41.040
and

01:26:41.040 --> 01:26:43.110
sleep that is robbed

01:26:43.120 --> 01:26:44.629
from you because you're always trying to

01:26:44.639 --> 01:26:46.149
think, 'I don't want to miss it. I don't

01:26:46.159 --> 01:26:47.510
want to miss it. I

01:26:47.520 --> 01:26:50.390
need to hear You, but You're

01:26:50.400 --> 01:26:52.470
quiet. I don't hear You.'I've been

01:26:52.480 --> 01:26:54.070
there. I know. And I was there

01:26:54.080 --> 01:26:55.590
recently. I said, 'What do I do? What do

01:26:55.600 --> 01:26:57.990
I do?'And I wanted an answer.

01:26:58.000 --> 01:26:59.270
And I thought, 'I hear You in the

01:26:59.280 --> 01:27:00.470
broadcast. I hear You, but You're not

01:27:00.480 --> 01:27:03.030
talking about my personal stuff. What's

01:27:03.040 --> 01:27:06.629
going on?'But He spoke when I took my

01:27:06.639 --> 01:27:09.830
eyes off of the problem and I put them

01:27:09.840 --> 01:27:12.950
on Him.

01:27:12.960 --> 01:27:15.910
How badly I wanted the answer! 'Oh, I need

01:27:15.920 --> 01:27:17.189
this answer. I need this.'I told

01:27:17.199 --> 01:27:18.950
Diana all day, 'I need this. I

01:27:18.960 --> 01:27:20.149
need Him. I don't know why He's not

01:27:20.159 --> 01:27:23.510
talking to me about this. He knows I

01:27:23.520 --> 01:27:25.990
need to know this.'And

01:27:25.990 --> 01:27:26.000
I was

01:27:26.000 --> 01:27:28.229
getting frustrated. And

01:27:28.229 --> 01:27:28.239
I thought,

01:27:28.239 --> 01:27:29.590
'Well, I hear You on this other

01:27:29.600 --> 01:27:30.870
stuff, and You want to talk about the

01:27:30.880 --> 01:27:34.950
weather?

01:27:34.960 --> 01:27:37.030
Why are You talking about the weather?'And

01:27:37.030 --> 01:27:37.040
I went,

01:27:37.040 --> 01:27:39.110
'Well, at least You're

01:27:39.110 --> 01:27:39.120
talking.'And

01:27:39.120 --> 01:27:40.629
I got quiet, but I said, 'But what

01:27:40.639 --> 01:27:45.590
about

01:27:45.590 --> 01:27:45.600
this?'Nothing.

01:27:45.600 --> 01:27:48.790
Just full of the care of

01:27:48.800 --> 01:27:51.030
it, just letting it eat me. And I was

01:27:51.030 --> 01:27:51.040
driving

01:27:51.040 --> 01:27:52.229
around. I got in the car. I said,

01:27:52.239 --> 01:27:53.669
'Well, we'll just go pray. We'll go get

01:27:53.679 --> 01:27:55.590
in the car. Paisley, let's go pray. Come

01:27:55.600 --> 01:27:57.110
on, D. Let's go get in the car. Braden,

01:27:57.120 --> 01:27:58.310
come on. We're going to go

01:27:58.310 --> 01:27:58.320
pray.'And

01:27:58.320 --> 01:27:59.830
I drove around for

01:27:59.840 --> 01:28:02.229
hours, driving around in the car, praying up

01:28:02.239 --> 01:28:04.070
and down Tulsa. 'Oh, God,

01:28:04.080 --> 01:28:05.750
You're going to give me the

01:28:05.750 --> 01:28:05.760
answer.'Worship.

01:28:05.760 --> 01:28:07.510
Worship. 'Oh, God, give me an

01:28:07.520 --> 01:28:08.950
answer.

01:28:08.960 --> 01:28:10.709
Paisley, you hear anything?

01:28:10.709 --> 01:28:10.719
Do

01:28:10.719 --> 01:28:18.950
you?''No.'But

01:28:18.960 --> 01:28:23.030
when I

01:28:23.040 --> 01:28:24.629
was at that breaking

01:28:24.639 --> 01:28:25.990
place, you know, you're just in there,

01:28:26.000 --> 01:28:28.070
and I went in and I told her,

01:28:28.080 --> 01:28:31.510
'I'm going to go out and pull

01:28:31.510 --> 01:28:31.520
weeds.'And

01:28:31.520 --> 01:28:33.110
I was done with it. I was like,

01:28:33.120 --> 01:28:34.229
'If You don't want to answer, it's not

01:28:34.239 --> 01:28:35.270
important to You. It's not important to

01:28:35.280 --> 01:28:36.550
me. I guess I'm not going to talk about

01:28:36.560 --> 01:28:39.306
this

01:28:39.316 --> 01:28:39.350
anymore.'And

01:28:39.360 --> 01:28:42.310
I'm out there pulling the weeds, and

01:28:42.320 --> 01:28:44.790
I'm looking at my flower in the

01:28:44.800 --> 01:28:48.149
flower bed, and I was thinking, 'Man,

01:28:48.159 --> 01:28:50.149
that's pretty amazing how fast these

01:28:50.159 --> 01:28:54.229
weeds are growing.'Pulling the weeds,

01:28:54.239 --> 01:28:56.149
and I just took my eyes off of the

01:28:56.159 --> 01:29:00.070
problem and started focusing on Him.

01:29:00.080 --> 01:29:01.350
'Well, I got to know what I'm going to

01:29:01.360 --> 01:29:02.709
say on the channel

01:29:02.709 --> 01:29:02.719
tonight.'I

